<view class='page'>
  <image src='../../../images/about_background.png' class='background'></image>
  <view class='top' bindtap='chooseImage'>
    <block wx:if="{{img_path}}">
      <image style="height:350rpx;" src="{{img_path}}" mode='center'></image>
    </block>
    <block wx:else>
    <van-icon
      name="photo-o"
      size='300%'
    />
    </block>
  </view>
  <view class='first'><text>👌广场页面会不定时分享一个选择卡片。如果你也有什么好玩的创意，欢迎提供给我们，可能就会出现在某天的广场上哦</text></view>
  
  <scrool-view style='margin-top:20rpx;width:100%;height:750rpx;'>
    <van-cell-group>
    <van-field
      type='textarea'
      autosize
      label='正面'
      placeholder="请输入卡片正面"
      bind:change="onChangeFace"
      title-width='50px'
      maxlength='200'
    />
    <van-field
      type='textarea'
      autosize
      label='左滑'
      placeholder="请输入左滑答案"
      bind:change="onChangeRight"
      title-width='50px'
      input-class='face'
      maxlength='100'
    />
    <van-field
      type='textarea'
      autosize
      label='右滑'
      placeholder="请输入右滑答案"
      bind:change="onChangeLeft"
      title-width='50px'
      maxlength='100'
    />
    </van-cell-group>
    <view class='bottom'>
      <button type='primary' bindtap='submit' loading='{{loading}}'>提交卡片</button>
    </view>
  </scrool-view>
  
  
</view>